{"tid":1437134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現 場 有 糾 察 有 咩 問 題 ？","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:47:38.000Z","uid":61511,"like":35,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"17bbd3af2cd78bf3c610c69ae7c63db641e45aac","tid":1437134,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"邊個授權糾察呀?<br />\n我地有咩權力阻止/監察佢地呀?<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個問題答案都係 <br />\n<br />\n無呀,係無呀<br />\n<br />\n點解反糾察=反大台呀<br />\n<br />\n因為糾察會幫手成立大台去進一步穩定自己既權力<br />\n有大台,有聲音 你多多大聲公都無用呀<br />\n<br />\n糾察起大台,大台護糾察<br />\n無限loop!<br />\n<br />\n咁唔同佢同意見既人呢?<br />\n唔好意思呀,你要收收皮啦,因為你把聲已經無人聽到啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個公海gp個admin<br />\n係囉唔知點解可以做到admin<br />\n<br />\n私底下同機管局商量<br />\n哪來的權力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另,第6點<br />\n自己睇啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrTihAh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrTihAh.png&h=4d10f1f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d379b83a0eaa0c14eeb18f169e6b30aad6167292","tid":1437134,"uid":61511,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nctupgi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnctupgi.png&h=758a46a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b641177ef489549dea11426c64ad2d821c3dd9a9","tid":1437134,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6bf5ca5b6b004a3a682dedc1b7986a06463ca5f","tid":1437134,"uid":107060,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"鄺仔佔中果時都係糾察"},{"pid":"65c56f3b7ae8363c81b1449ffc8c59d57b65d886","tid":1437134,"uid":61511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HfwCwa.png\" da